creator: Asteroid Game Studio
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to
Royal Indian wedding rituals makeup and salon

Royal Indian wedding rituals makeup and salon is Hindu traditional wedding ceremonies game...
Every bride wants to look amazing in her dream wedding.Every Indian princess want to look like bride in own wedding
In this game we have provided all in one wedding package from hair spa ,pedicure ,manicure,spa,card decoration, makeup,dressup, gajra, car decoration, dolly decoration, mandap decoration, wedding rituals and photoshoot.
Have fun playing this most rituals Indian marriage makeovers salon game and enjoy Royal Indian wedding rituals makeup and salon game.

Features:

Hair spa :
Know bride putting their best hair by booking hair care treatment before the big day. In hair spa treatments use shampoo, hair cutting, shower etc....

Pedicure View:
Bride can use different types of pedicure tools.

Manicure View:
Bride can use different types of pedicure tools.

Spa View:
Enjoy facial spa treatment to make her skin look bright and smooth using different facial product.

Card decorations:
Design the wedding invitation to warm up your wedding events. A custom invitation will impress your guests deeply and will be cherished forever.

Makeup View:
Every bride wants to look radiant on her wedding day in bridal makeup and plan for it in advance with number of elegant bridal makeup options which includes different hair styles,colourful eyeball ,eyelashes ,lipsticks ,blushes and bindis.

Gajara View:
Gajara is a flower garland that is used to enhance the beauty of hair of women.

Bride Dressup:
Create your own ethnic style with indian tradition outfits like chaniya choli and gowns and choose hair style,earrings,necklace,bangles, sandal and bindi to make special wedding.

Groom Dressup:
Every groom wants to look handsome in his wedding..here are a few essential grooming products like outfits,footwear,specs and head safa for groom.

Car Decoration:
Wedding car decoration involves car colours,car graphics and flower decoration.

Doli Decoration:
A doli is a suspended by four corners from bamboo pole. Decorate with different flower. And we modify that.

Mandap decoration:
The royal indian wedding Mandap is a crucial part of the Hindu marriage ceremony. We have more than eight decoration objects in this.

Wedding View:
When groom and bride round the fire, they give some promises to each other. Peoples pray to god for love and live long relation between them.

Photoshoot View:
Wedding photo is a very important Let's click the photo to make a wedding memorable.so click a memorable photo in this game .
descriptionShort: Royal Indian wedding rituals makeup and salon is wedding ceremonies game.
